data.description: Stunning 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath home with brand new roof, AC only 3 years old, and water heater is 4 years old. All major items on this home are brand new so no fret over insurance rates. This block stucco home sits on a corner lot, with a circular driveway in the front and side driveway going into the garage. Large backyard ready for a pool to entertain guests. Updated all throughout with large, spacious bedrooms. Large master bedroom is 20X11 with a his and hers closets and updated en-suite bathroom with shower. Guests' bedrooms are large as well with one on other side of home that is 18X7. Great for an office or guest bedroom with half bathroom adjacent to it. Wood burning fireplace is located in the open concept living room and dining room to entertain guests and have large family gatherings. The same laminate floors are all throughout the house with tile in the 3 bathrooms and luxury vinyl planks in the kitchen. Bay window in the living room. No HOA! So, bring your toys, your boat, your camper, your trailer, your work truck etc. This spacious home is great for a large family or smaller with room for an office or guest bedroom. No water intrusion from the 2022 historic 100-year flood hurricane. ;Water: City
